data.name: Black Tie Affair Gun
data.description: Pick from one of 5 suits and fire them at your friends and opponents.

data.name: Year of the Monkey Lantern
data.description: Celebrate the year of the monkey with this awesome lantern.  The spirit of monkey will protect you!

data.name: Epic Golden Sword and Shield
data.description: Click to swing dealing 15 to 22 damage; double click to spin-dash at your opponent while on fire!

data.name: M1 Garand
data.description: This M1 includes an eight-round clip, with bullets that deal 35 points of damage to the body and insta-kills for head shots.

data.name: 8-Bit Wizarding Staff
data.description: Wham, bam, alakazam! Click to spawn deadly fireballs at your foes.

data.name: Baby Nessie Mount
data.description: You’re a long way from your loch, friend.

data.name: Make It Rain
data.description: Making it rain has never been so easy!  Throw money around like it ain't no thang.  People near you when you make it rain will follow you around to pick money up.

data.name: Brighteyes's Sparkling Shillelagh
data.description: Made with solid oak, and sprinkled with some Brighteyes’s magic, this sparkling Shillelagh, will help you bend some bones! Watch out, this Shillelagh hits hard!

data.name: Radical Purple Keytar
data.description: Is this keytar totally radical? No duh! Just click to slam out a sick jam like a totally righteous dude.

data.name: Snow Storm Cloud
data.description: Clicking on a humanoid of any kind (yep, works on NPCs) will cause a cloud to rush from your hand to your target. It will hover above them, spin and occasionally drop snowflakes.

data.name: 2019 Spinning Noisemaker
data.description: Ring the new year in with as much noise as possible.

data.name: Giant Dinosaur Feet
data.description: Stomp around ROBLOX in these giant dino feet! Every step you take will do 10 damage to nearby foes and knock them back. If you manage to jump on someone's head while wearing these prehistoric bad boys, you'll stomp them until their health is gone.

data.name: Magnificent Magenta Paintball Gun
data.description: Everyone's screen can always use a little more magenta.

data.name: Viridian Hoverboard
data.description: Roll in high fashion with this stylish viridian board.

data.name: Bloxiade
data.description: As a Robloxian athlete, I know how important it is to stay hydrated.  I like to stay hydrated with Bloxiade.  I think it makes me run faster, and my coach does too!

data.name: Classic Plane
data.description: You'll go plane crazy for this awesome plane. Jump in and fly around ROBLOXIA.

data.name: 8-Bit Blaster
data.description: Pew pew pew! Shoot neon red lasers at enemies making a pew pew noise!

data.name: Trusty Blade
data.description: This well rounded sword is well suited for blocking daggers, but vulnerable to bigger blades.  Does 35 damage per attack.

data.name: Poseidon's Quake Trident
data.description: Shake the land and sea with Poseidon's Quake Trident!

data.name: Wooden Club
data.description: Cavemen used these to hunt their prey. I'm pretty sure they needed a bigger one for the woolly mammoths.

data.name: Leland the Lolturtle
data.description: Leland does it for the lulz.

data.name: Overseer Sword & Shield
data.description: Click to swing your sword forward, dealing between 22 and 25 damage. Double click to spawn green flames and lunge forward, dealing double the damage.

data.name: Knights of Redcliff: Battle Axe
data.description: When Redcliff Knights are proficient with the battle axe, their knight masters know they are ready for the next deadly challenge.

data.name: Saxophone
data.description: Saxomaphone....saxomaphone..tubamaphone?

data.name: Battle Bottle
data.description: This bottle is half full...of explosives.

data.name: Patriot's Monster Truck
data.description: It is your duty to drive over all other RC cars. Anything less would be Un-American.

data.name: Pool Noodle
data.description: Swing your pool noodle with all you've got!  Anyone it hits will be pushed back.

data.name: Dual Gravity Coil
data.description: Wear these awesome dual gravity coils on your feet for extra spring in your step!

data.name: Flaming Orb of Divine Pain
data.description: Cast deadly fireballs at your enemies with this orb. Enemies will be dealt anywhere from 25 up to 45 damage.

data.name: Cobalt Interplanetary Light Sword
data.description: Its power other planetary, its glow otherworldly...

data.name: BANG!
data.description: Does no damage, but that's not really the point is it?

data.name: Meteor Staff
data.description: Let the fires and stones of the sky rain down upon all who dare defy you.  If your opponent gets hit by one of the meteors you summon, he will meet a swift end.  Only you are protected from the shower of debris that will rain down when you summon it.

data.name: Towering Inferno Sword
data.description: Raise fire to the heavens!

data.name: Bluster Buster
data.description: Harness air power to defeat your foes!  I'm not talking about planes.

data.name: Present Launcher
data.description: With this, you can fully embrace the spirit of giving by launching gifts at people. If hit, your foes will receive 20 damage!

data.name: Clawknife
data.description: A sword with claws seems a little redundant to me, but whatever.

data.name: Skeleton King's Sword
data.description: This sword features three unique swings and a spin move (tap “W” twice and left-click), each of which has a 20% chance of cracking an enemy’s joints. As if that wasn’t enough, each attack has a 22% chance of being critical (2.25x damage). Normal attacks do 25 damage, landing critical attacks at about 56. Bone has never been so dangerous.

data.name: ROBLOX U Free Stuff Launcher
data.description: Stuff! People love stuff!  Launch free pizza and tee shirts from this cannon.

data.name: Great White Mount
data.description: Take a bite out of the sky with this hovering friendly shark.

data.name: Kunai
data.description: The weapon is small, the danger is great.

data.name: Beach Ball
data.description: Have a ball with this classic beach toy.

data.name: Paintball Pro
data.description: You are allied with no team.  You shoot for you.

data.name: Attack Sloth
data.description: He just wants a hug...a real slow one...Does 5 damage and slows down your opponents!

data.name: Blue Bloxxers Paintball Gun
data.description: Get ready for the bloxxing of a lifetime!

data.name: Heat Seeking Missile Launcher
data.description: Lock on to the enemy and fire for a one hit knock out.  4 second reload time.

data.name: Orinthian Electroslasher
data.description: Click to slash, dealing 16 to 20 damage. Hit the 'Q' key to spawn three Orinthian warrior minions in front of you, which will chase nearby enemies, dealing 10 damage per hit.

data.name: Blue Speedster
data.description: Drive this road-ready, raceable speedster with  'W', 'A', 'S', 'D', or the arrow keys.

data.name: Skeleton BattleAxe
data.description: Have axe, will slash.

data.name: Party Blaster Paint Gun
data.description: Ain't no party like a paint gun party, cuz it stains and it's hard to wash out. Fire paintballs of all different colors at your enemies!

data.name: Christmas Tree Sword
data.description: This dangerous holiday sword may look fun, but it will be anything but for your foe. Each hit will do 34 damage and if you manage to KO your opponent they'll be wrapped up like a gift.

data.name: Skeleton Slashers
data.description: Click to slash, dealing between 15 to 25 damage. Double click to dash forward and double-slash, using both arms. If you can hit your opponent with this attack, they take 30 points of damage!

data.name: Hockey Stick
data.description: Shoot pucks at your foes and check them into submission.

data.name: Moonwalk Dance Potion
data.description: We are here to change the world!

data.name: Bronze Kopesh
data.description: Standard issue for the ancient Egyptian infantry.

data.name: Dual Bacon Daggers
data.description: Bacon goes with everything! Even daggers.  Click to swing one of your daggers at your foe and do 15 damage. Double click to do a special bacon attack which does 20 damage.  Wear the bacon crown while using these daggers to do an additional 15 damage.

data.name: Classic Bucket
data.description: I has a bucket.  Nooo they be stealin' my Bucket.  This gear item is awesome for playing tag.

data.name: Machete
data.description: Hack through jungles with this machete. Eversharp!

data.name: Airstrike
data.description: Your foes don't stand a chance when you call your pilot friends for reinforcements!  Use this to call a jet fighter that launches missiles at any area you designate.

data.name: Korblox Bone Mace
data.description: Each swing of this powerful Korblox mace deals 15 damage. KO 3 players and transform yourself into a Korblox character with a super fast walk speed and extra damage capabilities.

data.name: Medusa Head
data.description: Turn your enemies to stone for 5 seconds with this frightning Medusa head.

data.name: Knight's Sword
data.description: Keep down the peasant uprisings with this gleaming longsword.

data.name: Robloxsai Bike
data.description: Now you can bike like Robloxsai!  Control your bike using 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D', or the arrow keys.

data.name: Zombie STOPing Axe
data.description: Stop a zombie attack DEAD in its tracks. Swing this axe at enemies; dealing 15 damage each hit.

data.name: First Class Fencing Sword
data.description: Fence your way to a gold medal with this first class sword.

data.name: Crossbow of the Sea
data.description: Shoots magical water arrows that spawn water wherever they hit.

data.name: Hot Dog
data.description: Challenge your friends to an awesome hot dog eating contest.  Regardless of who wins, it's going to be a fun time!

data.name: Zombie Dog
data.description: This loyal undead friend will poison any foe that gets in your way.

data.name: Tiger Friend
data.description: If a tiger is chasing you and your friend, you have only one chance at survival.  Trip your friend.

data.name: Rockin' Pink Guitar
data.description: Rock on! Use the keys 'Z', 'X', 'C', 'V', 'B', 'N', 'M', to play different chords. You can play sharp version of the notes by holding shift. You can alter the pitch as well with the keys 'G', 'H', 'J', 'K', 'L'.

data.name: Stravant's Lightning
data.description: Run like the wind and shoot deadly lightning beams at people. We're always having to tell him no lightning in the office...

data.name: Fencing Foil
data.description: En garde! This sword is very quick. It does high lunging damage but very low slashing damage.

data.name: Chocolate Gelt
data.description: Who knew money could be so yummy!

data.name: Yellow Card
data.description: Unsportmanlike Conduct!  One more time and you're out of here!

data.name: Mariachi Guitar
data.description: This is music made for dancing!

data.name: 4th of July Fireworks 2018
data.description: Celebrate the 4th with a BANG!

data.name: 8-Bit Duck Friend
data.description: No need to hunt for this duck, this faithful friend will spawn on click and follow you around. Click around nearby and he'll fly to that designated spot as well.

data.name: Red Laser Scythe
data.description: Red is the future. Slash this powerful laser scythe to do 30 damage per hit. Click and hold to do some animated swinging to unleash a laser projectile.

data.name: Black Hole Sword
data.description: Slash your foes into a despair so dark that even light cannot escape it.

data.name: Viridian Katana
data.description: Sometimes it is easy being green.  Easy to slash through foes, easy to win the battle, easy to win the war.

data.name: Attack Ocelot
data.description: "I've never seen an ocelot!" This ocelot companion follows you around and chases after enemies.

data.name: Alpaca Mount
data.description: Alpaca your bags, you're ready to ride! Equip to spawn in front of you and simply hop on. Walks at a normal pace; however can jump super high.

data.name: Teapot Launcher
data.description: Have you seen my teapot collection? Here, take a closer look.

data.name: Gravity Disruptor
data.description: Disrupt the battlefield!

data.name: Yellow Snowball
data.description: Ewww...  say no to yellow snow.

data.name: Valentine’s Throwing Stars
data.description: Throw deadly love at your enemies!

data.name: Sword of Glowing Hope
data.description: Even in the deepest darkness, there is hope in the flash of my blade. This sword is lit up so it's bright in dark places and slightly glows. Slash at your enemies dealing 17 damage per hit. Upon slashing enemies, sparks emit out of the sword. Anybody killed will burst into neon green flame particles and vanish.

data.name: Quick Potion
data.description: Zoom zoom!!!

data.name: Slingshot
data.description: It's a sure shot everytime!  Well only if you've got great aim....

data.name: Personal Fighter Jets
data.description: Mini jet fighters that strike at your command! They'll circle your head until you are ready to unleash the fury!

data.name: First Aid Kit
data.description: Why aren't they just called aid kits? Or bandaid boxes?  Why the word first?

data.name: Math Homework
data.description: I was doing my math homework and there was this problem about if a plane travels at 11x the speed of a train and the train is 3x.....blah blah blah...I made a plane!

data.name: Personal Rocketship
data.description: It's like a personal pizza but with no pepperoni and it costs five billion dollars.

data.name: DarkAge Ninjas: SunFire Scroll
data.description: Use the power of the scroll, to unleash a torrent of sunfire blast around you!

data.name: Wyldfang the Brave Companion
data.description: Now you're a two man wolf-pack.

data.name: Ro-torcycle
data.description: Ride around ROBLOX on your tricked out Ro-torcycle.  Features dynamically lit headlight and sweet rotating wheels.

data.name: Battle Slingshot
data.description: Battle your foes with this rapid firing slingshot!

data.name: Red Stratobloxxer
data.description: How to rock: 1) Equip Red Stratobloxxer. 2) Change notes by pressing [f,g,h,j,k,l] 3) Left click.

data.name: Go Fish
data.description: Challenge your friends to see who can catch the most fish!

data.name: Regular Carpet
data.description: You walk past a rug shop, where a clerk tries to sell you a magic carpet.  You tell him you don't want a magic carpet today. He then admits to you that he was lying, and this really is just a regular carpet. His whole life is a lie. Then he starts crying. You kind of have to buy it after that.  This is a regular carpet and it literally does nothing.

data.name: Birthday Pinata
data.description: Definitely makes my list of top 5 birthday activities!

data.name: ROBLOX U Foam Finger
data.description: Root, root, root for the home team!  Raise your foam finger in victory and high five other fans!

data.name: Ninja Whip
data.description: Keep calm and use your ninja whip.

data.name: Trololo Cape of Invisibility
data.description: Now you see me - now you don't!  Turns yourself invisible and reappear as if out of thin air!

data.name: Rainbow Laser Blaster
data.description: Click and hold rapidly fire neon lasers in all the colors of the rainbow.  Each laser does 12 damage on hit.

data.name: Chaos Master's Wing Slasher
data.description: Man may not fly in your presence.  Any person with wings will have them slashed by this sword and fall to their peril.  As for your enemies on the ground, they'll have a tough time escaping this swords speedy 24 damage hit.

data.name: Cowbell
data.description: MOAR COWBELL!

data.name: Dance Grenade
data.description: The roof, the roof, the roof is on fire!  The roof is on fire because you just set off this awesome dance grenade!

data.name: Forest Bow and Arrow
data.description: These bows, often given as gifts by forest elves, can be used by anyone regardless of skill with a bow. Click to shoot and leave a flurry of leaves in your arrow's wake.

data.name: Atmoshocker
data.description: ATMOSHOCKER!

data.name: Compass
data.description: Never get lost in a cave or maze again with this handy compass. Always points due north. A must for tomb raiders everywhere.

data.name: Midnight Sword
data.description: Slash at your foes to do 10 damage. Charge the sword by holding down the left mouse button to change day to night, increase your walk speed, and increase the damage your sword does.

data.name: Bluesteel Midas Hand
data.description: The Bluesteel Midas Hand will turn anything into beautiful Bluesteel!

data.name: 8-Bit Frog Friend
data.description: A faithful friend who follows you around, just keep him away from the road.

data.name: Drum Kit
data.description: Darthskrill's drum kit can be yours!  Rock out like JParty and the Meme Lords with this stylish kit.

data.name: Earth Protection Orb
data.description: Heal the world!  In ROBLOX - world heals you!  Well...it at least protects you!  This Earth orbits around you and shields you from nearby foes. Anyone who dares approach you will feel the burning wrath of core magma!

data.name: Death Run 2 Shoes
data.description: Equip to put these shoes on and increase your walk speed to 24.  Click to double your walk speed and jump super high for the next 30 seconds.

data.name: Steampunk Hoverboard
data.description: At long last, you can harness the mighty power of steam to give you the power of flight. Well more like the power to float close to the ground, but at high speeds. Ok well, high-ish speeds. It's definitely faster than walking.

data.name: Bear Mine Gun
data.description: With the Bear Mine Gun, you strategically place two “bear mines” and remotely trigger them to come together at a high velocity for an explosive bear hug, instantly killing anyone caught in the middle.

data.name: Holiday Ornament Staff
data.description: Send a giant holiday ornament hurling at your enemies to squish them.

data.name: Epicsauce
data.description: Ultimate EPIC Juice Brand Epicsauce. Extremely hot.

data.name: Disguise-to-Go Watch
data.description: It's TIME to disappear! Click to change into a random appearance, wearing random hats and clothing for a little while and confuse others!

data.name: Bug Juice
data.description: It doesn't come in a jar. It comes from who you are.  But seriously - this stuff will make you jump like there are 100 spiders after you.

data.name: Dance Potion
data.description: One sip gives you uncontrollable dance fever!

data.name: Laser Electrocutor
data.description: Don't laser electrocute me bro!

data.name: Vine Staff
data.description: Creates a wall of vines around your character. Anyone attempting to get through the vines tends to get stuck.

data.name: Pirate Cutlass
data.description: Avast!!

data.name: Deluxe Beach Ball
data.description: Hit the ball back and forth with friends.  Just another chill day on the ROBLOXIAN beachfront.

data.name: Intern Racing Chair 2014
data.description: 2014 interns race in style!  Ride this chair around and shoot rockets at your foes, all from the comfort of your ROBLOX office chair.

data.name: Spell Book of Ice Cold Revenge
data.description: Revenge is a dish best served cold. This spell lets you deliver vengeance in the coldest form: ice.

data.name: Gigantic Bat Wings
data.description: On leathery wings, you rule the night. Click to take flight and own the sky, using the 'W' 'A' 'S' and 'D' keys to move around.

data.name: Giant Kaiju Arms
data.description: Equip this gear to get monster-like arms. Clicking makes you punch, so you're ready for any fight.

data.name: Turkey Mount
data.description: Just like how the pilgrims used to ride turkeys at the first Thanksgiving. I saw it in a comic book.

data.name: Rapid Fire Snowflakes Shuriken
data.description: These rapid fire snowflakes deal 5-10 damage per hit.  If you can hit someone 5 times quickly, you'll freeze them in a block of ice for 20 seconds.

data.name: Razevenge
data.description: Razevenge is a dish best served cold.

data.name: Green Gremlins Paintball Gun
data.description: Go green with this awesome paintball gun!

data.name: Shadow Sword
data.description: Equipping the Shadow Sword shrouds your character in darkness. You immediately transform into a warrior wearing a jet-black suit and begin emitting a cloud of dark fog. While your appearance unnerves and disorients your opponents, each sword strike does 35 points of damage and pressing space twice teleports you forward.

data.name: Personal UFO
data.description: Drive your own personal UFO with up to 8 passengers! Use 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D' or arrow keys to control the direction and 'Q' to raise the UFO, 'E' to lower it. Click and hold to suck up players beneath you into the ship and press 'T' while they are in the beam to teleport players into an open seat on your UFO. Use ' L' to control your sweet UFO lights.

data.name: Foul Poison Fowl
data.description: Shoots poisonous green fire!  Equip the Poison Fowl and watch as it flies around you in a defensive circle, shooting at nearby enemies (25 damage per hit) for as long as five minutes.

data.name: Transmorph Ray Gun
data.description: Morph other players into objects.  Guy spawnkilling you?  Turn him into a hat, or an apple, or some other crazy thing!

data.name: Bacon Launcher
data.description: Equip this awesome bacon launcher to start cooking that sizzling bacon. Click to fire bacon at your foes.

data.name: Military Dress Sword
data.description: Sword of honor, sword of might, strike the right foe tonight.  This sword slashes and lunges.  For a special attack press 'W' twice before striking.

data.name: Lincoln's Golden Rail Splitter
data.description: Split any brick into dozens of pieces!  May or may not actually split bricks.

data.name: Dynamically Lit Sword
data.description: Darkness strikes in the light!  Swing your glowing sword at your foes to do 25 damage per hit.

data.name: Eggstermination Slingshot
data.description: Sling eggs at your friends and foes to cover their screen in eggs. It's a great yolk!

data.name: Sand Tempest Scimitar
data.description: In the lost desert kingdoms, three things are eternal: fire, sand, and steel.

data.name: Korblox Sword and Shield
data.description: The Korblox both fight and defend with stony spikes.

data.name: Festive Dueling Piano
data.description: One simple click will send this festive holiday piano crashing down from the sky and onto your target.  They'll get crushed and be unable to move while you play them a little holiday tune.

data.name: Elegant Blade
data.description: From a more civilized age.

data.name: Board With a Nail in It
data.description: Did they? That board with a nail in it may have defeated us. But the humans won't stop there. They'll make bigger boards and bigger nails, and soon, they will make a board with a nail so big, it will destroy them all!

data.name: Ultraviolet Blaster
data.description: Pew! Pew! Neon magenta laser beams are everywhere, but you don't care because you're the one shooting them! This weapon is good for shooting things from a distance. Hit 'Z' to activate the scope and use the mouse to zoom in and get a better view of the target.

data.name: First Aid Kit
data.description: It was hard, but you graduated college with a 4.2 GPA and got into a decent med school. Then you slogged through 4 more years of memorizing random facts. THEN you slaved away through 4 years of residency. THEN you got drafted by the army and make $45,000 a year. NOW you run around like mad, flinging medkits at your team mates just trying not to get shot. Yes. Law school was the right choice. You owned yourself.

data.name: Rolling Pin
data.description: Your grandma uses this to make pies.  What will you use it for?

data.name: Boomerang
data.description: Enjoy a nice peaceful game of catch... with yourself or a friend!

data.name: Deluxe Mechatronic Spider
data.description: Click to spawn six deadly spiders. They will chase after any enemy daring enough to go near them. They deal five damage per hit, with six deadly spiders that adds up quickly! If close enough, they will shoot lasers from their robotic eye at you!

data.name: Rock Thunder
data.description: Your guitar has the lightning, now it's time to bring the thunder! You're gonna rock this stage. Change the chord using the keys, 'Z', 'X', 'C', 'V', 'B', 'N', 'M'. Alter the pitch using the keys 'G', 'H', 'J', 'K', 'L'. Hold shift to sharpen the chords. Complete the synchronized pattern of notes special (hit the ctrl key to begin) with at least 75% accuracy to shoot out non-lethal blue lightning.

data.name: Dual Plungers
data.description: Click and hold to become a plunger firing machine!

data.name: Wizard Flight Spell
data.description: Take flight with this magic spell!  Jump to begin flight; control using 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D', or the arrow keys. Hit the space bar again to stop flying.

data.name: DarkAge Bo Staff
data.description: Slash at your foes with a bo staff to do 15 damage.  Show off your extreme prowess by hitting the 'Q' key to activate the special attack - summon a line of deadly purple flames that will flow in any direction you face.

data.name: 2018 Fireworks
data.description: Happy 2018!!

data.name: All-Seeing Golem's Hammer
data.description: Click to swing and deal 15 damage per hit. Double click to do a powerful hammer slam which will create a massive shockwave.

data.name: Deluxe Vine Staff
data.description: Call forth a circle of vines from the earth.  If your foes hit them they will do 20 damage.

data.name: Atomizer
data.description: Split yourself into pieces to evade your enemies!

data.name: Ferocious Mr. Fox
data.description: The swiftest of mounts, the most cunning of steeds.

data.name: Staff of Eggstra Large Eggs
data.description: Summon a giant flaming egg from the sky which will crash down and fling your foe far from his current location.

data.name: Sword of Starlight
data.description: You have the power of stars!

data.name: Penguin Horde  Attack
data.description: Click to drop penguins who will attack your foes- doing 15 damage per hit.

data.name: NobleDragon's Noble Dragon
data.description: If well taken care of, your Noble Dragon will follow you around and shoot flames at anyone who dares to approach you! We recommend feeding your Noble Dragon only coffee and dreams (this keeps it in prime condition!) but it's a virtual pet. Pixels are pixels!

data.name: Dueling Piano
data.description: One simple click will send this piano crashing down from the sky and onto your target.  They'll get crushed and be unable to move while you play them a little tune.  Is it a duel if only one of you has a piano? Only one way to find out.

data.name: Snowy Gravity Coil
data.description: As you walk, leave behind a trail of ice, and as you leap, the north wind gives you a boost the whole way, lifting you high and dropping you gently.

data.name: Staff of Sparks
data.description: This staff shoots mini ball-lightnings.

data.name: Arabian Knight Scimitar
data.description: "Son of infamy! Every bone in your body shall be broken if you continue to defy me!"

data.name: Tee Shirt Cannon
data.description: Shoots tee-shirts at your friends and has them wear the shirts you shot.  You can even customize which shirts come out of the cannon.

data.name: Leprechaun Harp
data.description: The harp that once through Tara's halls / The soul of music shed / Now hangs as mute on Tara's halls / As if that soul were fled / So sleeps the pride of former days / So glory's thrill is o'er / And hearts that once beat high for praise / Now feel that pulse no more

data.name: Squid Launcher
data.description: Launch everyone's favorite squid, Mr.Tentacles at your enemies to obscure their screens in ink while doing 15 damage per hit. The squid will wrap its tentacles around your enemies head and shoot ink in their face!

data.name: Boxing Glove Launcher
data.description: Shoot dangerous boxing gloves at your foes.  They'll probably see it coming... but that's half the fun!

data.name: Guitar of Rock Excellence
data.description: For those about to rock, we salute you. Use the keys: 'Z', 'X', 'C', 'V', 'B', 'N', and 'M'. to play different tunes. Hold shift while pressing to sharpen the notes.

data.name: Orinthian Blaster 3777
data.description: Blast your enemies into the next galaxy  with the Orinthian blaster.  Does 35 damage per hit.

data.name: Orinthian Axe
data.description: Swing it at your foes to do Orinthian level damage, or use the special attack to throw a trail of signature Orinthian blue deathbricks.

data.name: Latke
data.description: Pass the apple sauce plz....

data.name: Positronic Platform Producer
data.description: Has a wall got you down, literally? Combat gravity the old-fashioned way with Positronic Platform Producer! Simply shoot at a wall to create a platform to stand on. Don’t get too comfortable though, as converting energy into mass can still prove to be a bit unstable, especially with walls that contain anchoritium.

data.name: Helen The Hiphipapotamus
data.description: Meet Helen, the Hiphipapotamus. Helen is the #1 toy in Robloxia and if you want to find her in a toy store, you better be packing heat to deal with all the other crazy parents trying to buy one.

data.name: Call Me Cellphone
data.description: It's not a request.

data.name: Spring Sunshine
data.description: You're just all sunshine and flowers!  Literally!  Bring the sun and have flowers grow everywhere you go.

data.name: Emerald Knights of the Seventh Sanctum Staff
data.description: Use the magical power of Emeralds to immobilize and shock your target!

data.name: Hand Cannon

data.name: Bundle of TNT
data.description: Industrially, TNT is synthesized in a three-step process. First, toluene is nitrated with a mixture of sulfuric and nitric acid to produce mono-nitrotoluene or MNT. The MNT is separated and then renitrated to dinitrotoluene or DNT. In the final step, the DNT is nitrated to trinitrotoluene or TNT using an anhydrous mixture of nitric acid and oleum. Nitric acid is consumed by the manufacturing process, but the diluted sulfuric acid can be reconcentrated and reused. Subsequent to nitration, TNT is stabilized by a process called sulphitation, where the crude TNT is treated with aqueous sodium sulfite solution in order to remove less stable isomers of TNT and other undesired reaction products. The rinse water from sulphitation is known as red water and is a significant pollutant and waste product of TNT manufacture.

data.name: Hiccup's Flaming Sword - Sponsored by HTTYD2
data.description: What every dragon trapper needs. One end coats the blade in Monstrous Nightmare saliva, the other sprays Hideous Zippleback gas!  Learn how to code your dragon - check out the video on the Bloxcon page http://www.roblox.com/event/bloxcon.

data.name: Knights of Redcliff: Sword and Shield
data.description: Second only to the infamous Redcliff Archers, the Redcliff Knights who wield the sword and shield, are fast and efficient.  They see their target, and they take him out in 5 swipes or less.

data.name: Admiral's Cutlass - A Walmart Exclusive!
data.description: Get this for free when you redeem a Walmart gamecard in June 2011!  It is said that the admiral rose quickly throught the ranks because of his superior swordsmanship.  But perhaps it was the sword itself?

data.name: Exploding Lab Table
data.description: You're a mad scientist.  You want to blow things up.  What could look more innocent than an exploding lab table?  Drop your portable lab anywhere and 10 seconds later watch everything explode!

data.name: Ocherous Katana of the Setting Sun
data.description: I am anti-life, the beast of judgement. I am the dark at the end of everything. The end of universes, gods, worlds... of everything. And what will you be then, Dreamlord?

data.name: Experimental Jetpack
data.description: Fresh out of R&D is our Jetpack prototype! Downside: only lets you jump far. Brightside: issue that kept exploding test subjects has been fixed!

data.name: Adventure Island
data.description: Check out the latest and best new 2D game on ROBLOX.  Explore and survive on Adventure Island!  Use "ASWD" keys to move, "W" to jump, "Enter" to shoot, and "Enter" + "W" to superjump.

data.name: ROBLOX Summer Sparkler
data.description: Click this item to shoot sparkles into the sky!

data.name: Explosive Super Glider
data.description: With the click of a mouse you are airborne. While in the air, you can drop deadly bombs on your enemies. The bombs do 100 damage per hit, but they have a small radius.  Aim carefully.

data.name: Faux Firebrand
data.description: The magical weapon of the Brothers Ignis, a 1000-strong force of battlehardened shocktroops.

data.name: Sabacc Playing Cards
data.description: A deck of Sabacc cards that can be enjoyed when you watch Solo: A Star Wars Story, in theaters May 25!

data.name: Neon Bloxster 2XP
data.description: Ride all over ROBLOXIA. Hit 'H' to honk and turn your headlight on and off with the 'X' key.

data.name: Gear Recycler
data.description: Everything old is new again! Put a gear item in, get a gear item of similar type out!

data.name: hicup789's ROBLOX Tablet
data.description: Winner: hicup789. ROBLOX will be in touch to redeem this prize. Void if sold, traded, or deleted.

data.name: Knight's Elder Blade
data.description: It is said that the Knights, once wielded blades that grew stronger as an enemy’s morale weakens. Time to test your knighthood!

data.name: Tiny Pony Stampede
data.description: Summon upon a stampede of ponies to charge at your enemies with lethal force!  Click and drag to summon the ponies and indicate their starting point and running direction.

data.name: Roblox Surfboard
data.description: Cruise around the beaches lookin’ hotter than the weather, riding with your surfboard! (Surfboard!)

data.name: Summertime Water Balloon
data.description: The best way to cool off is to stay hydrated. (At least that’s what you should tell your friends when you bombard them with water balloons)

data.name: Hula Dog
data.description: He thinks it's always Aloha Friday.

data.name: Incredibles 2 Badge
data.description: This is a signet justice and activating it lets you pursue evil even faster! Be sure to see Disney/Pixar’s Incredibles 2, in theatres June 15!

data.name: Skele-tar
data.description:
Columbus he set sail to find out if the world was round /
He kept on sailing west until he ran aground /
He thought he'd found the Indies, but he found the U.S.A. /
I know some navigators who can still do that today

data.name: Cupcake Launcher
data.description: I personally think that most cupcakes are too delicious to be launching at people's faces, but I can understand that some people disagree.

data.name: Rapid Launch Blaster
data.description: I don't fire laser guns often, but when I do, I want to do it rapidly.

data.name: Director's Clapboard
data.description: Aaaaand ACTION! Click to clap the boards and push enemies backwards!

data.name: d4rk886's ROBLOX Tablet
data.description: Winner: d4rk886. ROBLOX will be in touch to redeem this prize. Void if sold, traded, or deleted.

data.name: Bat Knight Bat Sword
data.description: You would think that you wouldn't need to use the word "Bat" so many times to name a sword.

data.name: Spartan Sword and Shield
data.description: THIS IS ROBLOX!!!!!!!! Use this sword on your enemy and when they have less than 25% health - kick them into a pit of doom.

data.name: Land Shark Shooter
data.description: Shoots out sharks that lurk beneath the land. Aim a shark at your foe and he'll never see it coming... unless he can see through the ground.

data.name: Telamon's Foe Hammer
data.description: For when a ban hammer just doesn't hit hard enough.

data.name: Breath of Fire
data.description: Swallow the flames and spit out fireballs at your foes!

data.name: Overseer Crossbow
data.description: Click and hold to rapidly fire arrows at your foes. Hit the 'Q' key to activate the Overseer's Menacing Arrow. Once fired, a massively sized Overseer Eye will magically replace the arrow and explode into hundreds of tiny eyes, which will shoot in all directions!

data.name: Golden Katana of Destiny
data.description: Do you fulfill the sword's golden destiny or does it help you fulfill yours?

data.name: Elixir of Dreams
data.description: In a dream - you're stronger and faster.  This potion makes your dream a reality. Be careful when holding this potion.  When dropped, it has a very different effect.

data.name: Scepter of Divine Indignation
data.description: Call upon the might of the heavens, infused into near-unstoppable orbs of power. Features three different modes for added variety when you’re obliterating all that stands in your way.

data.name: Knights of the Seventh Sanctum : Dual Duel Axes
data.description: You're dueling.  Your opponent has an axe... but you have two!  Wield the unholy relics of the Seventh Sanctum and no one else stands a chance... unless they have these axes too.  But how likely is that?

data.name: Mackerel
data.description: Holy Mackerel! This fish smarts!

data.name: Sir Lancelot’s Sword
data.description: Do centuries amounts of damage with this sword.  Exclusively fit for a Knight of the roundtable. Check out Night at the Museum: Secret of the Tomb in theaters December 19th!

data.name: Dastardly Skate
data.description: Top prize for the Big Air skate park building contest.

data.name: Slime Potion
data.description: Obtain this potion for some special power, sponsored by Nickelodeon Kids’ Choice Awards.

data.name: Golden Bow and Arrow
data.description: This golden bow is stylish and effective.  Click and hold to charge your arrows and increase the damage your arrow does! When you hit your enemy with a fully charged arrow they will turn into solid gold for 15 seconds. Press 'Q' to use the bow as a grappling hook.

data.name: Raig Chair
data.description: It's time for your foes to take a seat.... as they get hit by this chair!

data.name: Noxious Chocolate
data.description: Share this candy with your enemies.  Forces them to eat the candy (which is poisonous) and causes them to drop their weapons!

data.name: Star Butterfly’s Magic Wand
data.description: We don’t know how this wand works. We asked Star and she doesn’t either. But bad guys want it to take over the universe, so it must be special.

data.name: Big Bag of Bucks
data.description: A big bag of money is always useful for funding an adventure or bribing your way out of a tricky situation.

data.name: Advanced Exploding Lab Table
data.description: A lab table fit for a senior mad scientist. Click to drop the table where you're standing. A few seconds later, it explodes! The table breaks apart and pieces flung everywhere as well as dangerous chemicals.

data.name: Ice Potion
data.description: It's a slippery slope with this potion.  Even if it's not a slope!

data.name: Flame Guard General Sword
data.description:
Click to swing the sword and spawn a row of red ice crystals out in front of you. They'll burst in flames and anybody too close and hit by the shards is dealt 10 damage per hit! The closer you are to these, the more dangerous they are.

Part of the Flame Guard General package.

data.name: Tic Tac Toe Board
data.description: Play a quick game of Tic Tac Toe with a nearby player! (Get close to another player and click on them to start a game - they need to accept your challenge for the game to start).

data.name: Aquaman's Trident
data.description: A symbol of power and royalty, possession of this is proof of your status as a hero! Also, be sure to see Aquaman, in theaters December 21!

data.name: iLift
data.description: Next time someone asks - "Do you even lift?"  You can let them know exactly how much you lift... with a bar bell to the belly.

data.name: Scatterblaster
data.description: Think of it as a one-handed shotgun from the future. Good against masses of enemies, especially in tight corridors.

data.name: Formula R Remote Control Car
data.description: Simply click the steering wheel of the RC Car to deploy (or click again to bring it back to you), and use the regular walking keys (WASD) to move your new vehicle.

data.name: Lightning Orb
data.description: Summon lightning to stun your enemies!

data.name: Golden Bloxxer
data.description: So many KOs, so little time.  This trophy was awarded to the ultimate bloxxers of 2014. Three cheers for the golden bloxxers!  This item will be awarded to the top 1000 competitors in the 2014 Clan Battle Arenas.

data.name: Incinerator 6000
data.description: Why 6000?  Because it shoots fireballs that are a solid 6000 degrees of burning power.  Hold the mouse to charge your shot for maximum fire power!  This fire will damage any player it touches - doing 70 damage over 5 seconds.

data.name: Hard Boiled Roadster
data.description: Hop into this egg-shaped car and speed down the bunny trail!

data.name: Earth Summoning Horn
data.description: Blow upon this mighty relic to summon a massive earthquake within a 30 stud radius of where you're standing. Unanchored bricks begin to shake and break apart, and players trip and fall to the ground, slowly losing health. Three shockwaves are sent out, dealing around 20 damage per hit.

data.name: Blade of Marmora
data.description: The weapon of an secret group of resistance fighters committed to opposing the tyranny of the Galra Empire. Wield it with honor!

data.name: Blue Yonder
data.description: Catch some Big Air

data.name: The Unicorn Mace
data.description: This mace is known for dolling out punishment and a great way to fight fire with fire. Now hold tight, it ain’t over till it’s over.

data.name: The Axe of Undoing: A Walmart Exclusive
data.description: This axe will be the undoing of everything!  Awarded when you redeemed a card from Walmart in March, 2012.

data.name: Binoculray
data.description: Binoculrays allow you to see further than you've ever been able to before.  They're so powerful, you'll even be able to see through walls.

data.name: DarkAge Naginata
data.description: Fight with the strength and power of the DarkAge Ninjas.

data.name: Emerald Knights of the Seventh Sanctum Spellbook
data.description: Use the spell contained in this book to help stabilize the warring clans of ROBLOX.  Click to summon a protective shield that you can then fire at enemies.

data.name: Drachenstein The Guardian
data.description: Drachenstein The Guardian will follow you and shoot fire at anyone who comes near you.

data.name: MonStar
data.description: This is advertising. And a new companion coming through like a train. Be Real? But being imaginative is so much more coolio to jam with!

data.name: Protest: ROBLOXians Against SOPA
data.description: ROBLOX is against online censorship. Read our full position on SOPA/PIPA here: http://blog.roblox.com/2012/01/stop-online-piracy-act-sopa-and-roblox-our-stance/. If you agree, show your support with this sign!

data.name: Holiday Ham
data.description: Best way to stay healthy and strong this holiday season?  Enjoy some of this holiday ham!  Doubles your health!

data.name: Solid Gold Skateboard
data.description: Why buy gold plated when you can have solid gold. You deserve the best.  This sweet board emits golden sparkles when you're going at top speeds.

data.name: Nuclear Winter Icicle Gun
data.description: Your February 2010 Winter Contest entry was so hot, it was radioactive!

data.name: Captain America's Civil War Shield
data.description: Vibranium Shield used by Captain America in his fight for justice! After you claim your prize be sure to check out Captain America: Civil War on May 6th!

data.name: Spring Saber
data.description: Every rose has its thorn. Swing at your enemies dealing roughly 17 damage per hit!

data.name: Video Star Pizza Launcher
data.description: What's better than having your pizza delivered?  Having your favorite YouTuber launch it at you with a special prize.

data.name: Insert Tool
data.description: An Insert tool for building with sets

data.name: Rey’s Lightsaber
data.description: A lightsaber with a rich history in the Star Wars galaxy!

data.name: Are200's ROBLOX Tablet
data.description: Winner: Are200. ROBLOX will be in touch to redeem this prize. Void if sold, traded, or deleted.

data.name: Flying Magic Carpet
data.description: Fly through the skies of ROBLOXia on this magical carpet.

data.name: Noble RedCliff Eagle
data.description: To aid in the grand war against the Korbloxian Zombies, the faithful companion of the Knights of RedCliff follows its Master to the battlefield. With the strength of the Zombies ever increasing, the Eagle of RedCliff's help is definitely necessary for any and every Knight.

data.name: Paper Sword
data.description: Okay - let's be real here - a paper sword does as much damage as well....paper.  But it does do some other silly stuff.

data.name: Red LAZER Sword
data.description:
Sword meets future laser tech. Just like we always dreamed. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out www.roblox.com/toys to learn more...

data.name: Year of the Dog Lantern
data.description: Happy Lunar New Year! Celebrate with your own ghostly guard dog to protect you.

data.name: Fallen Artemis Sword & Shield
data.description: When equipped this shield doubles your current and max health. Click to slash for 15 damage per hit.  The special attack repeatedly strikes enemies for 30 damage per hit, one hit per second. Release the left mouse button while charging the do a double slash for 15 damage per hit.

data.name: The Blade of the Federation
data.description: The official weapon used in the Wars of Reunification.

data.name: Tomahawk
data.description: Long distance danger - free of charge!

data.name: Camping Lantern
data.description: Reading in your tent....brought to you by lanterns.  Dynamically lit lanterns.

data.name: Alien Parasite
data.description: Steals your enemy's health and replenishes your own!

data.name: TMNT Skateboard
data.description: TMNT Skateboard: Grab a skateboard to ride through the streets of ROBLOX, TMNT style!

data.name: Turbo's Speed Shell
data.description: Do you dream of going fast? Grab Turbo's Speed Shell for instant acceleration!

data.name: Monster Mash Dance Potion
data.description: You'll be a graveyard smash with this thrilling dance potion.

data.name: Flute
data.description: Time to go out enjoy the breeze  and play some soothing music! Watch as you play the flute, nearby Robloxians dancing to your tune!

data.name: Tarantula Pet
data.description: Click to summon a giant tarantula! A loyal friend, he'll follow you around until you command him to attack your enemy! Then, he'll chase after the enemy, shooting cobwebs at him. Once a web successfully strikes your foe, 25 damage is dealt and a large spiderweb wraps around his head, blinding him and slowing him down for 8 seconds. Now that your enemy is pretty much defenseless, this is when the tarantula goes in for the kill. Charging at your enemy, dealing 15 damage per hit.

data.name: Orbital Flute Strike
data.description: Imagine for a moment, you are peacefully playing a beautiful melody on your flute, when suddenly you see a flaming missile.  You realize that you are controlling its direction with your sweet music.  Where do you send it? That choice is yours and yours alone.

data.name: Orinthian Falcon
data.description: A noble guardian to help protect you on your quest.  And by protect, I mean attack all enemies.  Circles above you and attacks those enemies unfortunate enough to be selected as his prey.  This falcon is from the future and features 5 different attack modes.

data.name: Developer Pizza Launcher
data.description: Get a freshly delivered pizza from a developer participating in the Pizza Party event and earn an awesome prize!

data.name: Steelshanks Armament
data.description: Pirates don't fight fair. They bring guns to sword fights.

data.name: Chupacabra
data.description: You've captured the mystical chupacabra and now he does your bidding.   He still disappears on occasion, but when you click, he will attack your foes.  If you click another character, the chupacabra will attack it until it dies.

data.name: Dog Man Virtual Book
data.description: It's Dog Man, the crime-biting canine who is part dog, part man, and ALL HERO! Read the book to learn more!

data.name: Phantom Forces Combat Knife
data.description:
Looking for a fight? This is sharp, intimidating, and shiny. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out www.roblox.com/toys to learn more...

data.name: Frozen Blue Ice Crossbow
data.description: Fire ice cold arrows at your foes, which will occasionally freeze them upon hit. Each hit does 20 damage.

data.name: Bladed Ninja Claw
data.description: Click to slash at foes with your deadly dangerous ninja claw. Click and hold to charge the claw for an extra dangerous attack.

data.name: Admin Pizza Launcher
data.description: Admins! Join the party during our community event to give a special prize!

data.name: Sword of the Highlander
data.description:
And there's fire in the glen, fire in the glen /
But no fire in the eyes of our Highland men

data.name: DarkAge Ninja Bow
data.description: Click and hold to charge the arrow, the longer you charge, the more powerful the arrow gets. Max damage is between 15 and 55, depending on the charge. Hit 'Q' key to activate the special DarkAge Ninja attack for the ages! This attack rains arrows from the sky around your target.

data.name: The Luck O' the Irish
data.description: You just got McPwned.

data.name: Lava XD
data.description: This skateboard was awarded to builders who scorched the Urban Skate Jungle building contest in March 2010.

data.name: Neon 80s Boombox
data.description: Part of the Neon Party Guy package.

data.name: Deluxe Blue Roped
data.description: This stylish blue roped will keep you traveling in deluxe style.  It moves faster than the red roped and does sweet jumps with more ease than ever before.

data.name: Black Panther - Spear
data.description: Obtain the spear to be swift. Can you complete the missions faster than everyone? See Marvel Studio’s Black Panther in theaters February 16!

data.name: Power Gloves
data.description: Some people like to talk big and flex, others prefer to settle it in the square. Want to ring the bell? Ding, ding.

data.name: Interplanetary Light Sword
data.description: It glows with an otherworldly power...

data.name: Blast-a-ton - A Level Up Contest Prize
data.description: Use the Blast-a-Ton to shoot all kinds of things at your enemies.  Will it be poison darts, a rabid dog, confetti?  Who knows?

data.name: Civil War Artillery
data.description: Equip and click this gear to drop a real live cannon in front of you.  Control the cannons direction with the 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D' keys - lift and lower it with the cannon with the 'Q' and 'E' keys.  When you've got your shot set up - sit on the cannon and click! Hitting the 'X' key will remove it from the map.

data.name: Double Damage Frog
data.description: Throw this double damage frog at your foes. If it hits them, his poison rubs off on them and they turn blue for twenty seconds!  Any damage you do to them during this time is doubly effective!

data.name: ROBLOXIAN Healing Orb
data.description: Heal yourself with this glowing green orb.  No need to heal right now?  Drop healing orbs around a game and pick them up as needed. Why green?  Everyone knows that green is the color of healing...duh.

data.name: Flak Cannon
data.description: Designed for advanced players, this weapon is extremely powerful if you get the timing just right.  Mess it up?  You might just end up with a wipe out.

data.name: Laser Gun of Tomorrow
data.description: Click to fire a burst of 5 neon teal colored lasers! Each do 8 damage. If all 5 hit their target, that's a total of 40 damage!

data.name: Golden Sword of Spring Growth
data.description: Spring is here and gold is best. Best your foes by slashing them or by spawning a deadly field of protective poisonous flowers.  Click to slash and do 30-35 damage per hit. Press 'Q' to  spawn a deadly field of white, blue, gold, and violet flowers around you, preventing your enemies from coming up to you. Anyone that attempts to enter the field of flowers will be massively damaged every second they're in it.

data.name: Orinthian Sword and Shield
data.description: Slash enemies with your futuristic sword or stop them dead in their tracks with a shield bash!  Activate the shield bash stun with a right click to stun enemies for 2 seconds.  When enemies are stunned, you can do extra damage!

data.name: Knights of the Splintered Sky: Sword and Shield
data.description: The Knights of the Splintered Sky have descended to ROBLOX to help the Knights of Redcliff defeat the evil Zombies.  Are you brave enough to join them?

data.name: Sapphire Rapid Fire Shocker
data.description: Shock your foes into defeat with this rapid fire blaster!

data.name: Video Star Egg Launcher
data.description: Find your favorite video star and get an exclusive egg! Works only in the Egg Hunt 2019: Scrambled in Time hub world.

data.name: Merely's Web Slinger
data.description: Nobody slings web like Merely.  Nobody. Srsly.

data.name: Imaginary Companion
data.description: When imaginary friends start to become real, when they rattle windows and chains, begin to menace and terrify…Run, for that is no friend.

data.name: Bloxster STB
data.description: Leave 'em in the sparkles and dust.

data.name: 8-Bit Throwing Barrel
data.description: They'll never get the princess now! MUAHAHAHAHA

data.name: Trollin' Pumpkin
data.description: "Everyday I'm trollin' / Trollin' Trollin" Trololololo

data.name: Knights of the Splintered Skies: Bow and Arrow
data.description: While their strength lies in their speed and mobility, the Knights of the Splintered Skies are no less skillful in their ability to wield the bow. Blessed with purity of light, their arrows pierce through their enemies and lights them in skyfire, slowing them down and doing massive damage over time.

data.name: ROBLOX Rally Award 2011
data.description: These went out to some of the best game developers on ROBLOX.  Awarded at the ROBLOX Rally 2011.

data.name: Sword of the Raven's Feather
data.description: Light as a feather, sharp as a tack. Slash your foes with the dark power of the raven.

data.name: Spider Slasher
data.description: Click to slash double-click to lunge and do 12 damage. When you lunge, you also shoot a web in the the direction of your cursor. If it hits somebody, their speed is reduced to 6 for a few seconds, giving you an opportunity to catch up to them. While slashing your enemy with the sword, there is a 30% chance of poisoning them!

data.name: Cupid's Beloved Blade
data.description: In addition to dealing five points of damage per strike, this blade turns your opponent into a lovely shade of pink! Double tap "W" for a spin attack, double click for a homing attack, or press "A", "W", then "D" for a "pinksplosion"! Each special attack does 10 hit points of damage.

data.name: Sonic Boom Tuba
data.description: Loud doesn't even begin to describe it.

data.name: Ghost Hoverboard
data.description: Finally- the future I was promised is here!  Hoverboards!  Because ghosts are too cool to skateboard.

data.name: Snake Sniper
data.description: Shoot snakes from a snake. Your foes will never see it coming... okay they might.  You are shooting a snake from a snake after all.

data.name: White Sword Cane
data.description:
A cane to steady your gait when walking, and to eliminate your foes when fighting. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a code from a Roblox toy!

Check out www.roblox.com/toys to learn more...

data.name: Ice Cream Skateboard
data.description: That's one sweet board, bro.

data.name: Eggveloper Cannon 9002
data.description: After working countless hours on the event, you can let your anger out by launching eggs in the faces of unsuspeggting players!

data.name: Silver Bloxxer
data.description: You've bloxxed around the clock, and now, victory is yours!  This item will be awarded to the top 10,000 competitors in the 2014 Clan Battle Arenas.

data.name: Korblox Battlefield Trap
data.description: Place these traps along the battlefield to catch your enemy off guard!

data.name: Tornado Summoner
data.description: Summon the might of the air and unleash a wave of cyclones on anyone near you.  When these gale force winds are summoned close to foes, they're sure to be blown away!

data.name: RDC 2017 Winner Trophy
data.description: This exclusive trophy was awarded to the top three finalist teams during the RDC 2017 Game Jam, honoring their outstanding achievement in Roblox development.

data.name: RoboDog
data.description: All the fun of a dog without ever having to worry about remembering to feed it. And if it keeps barking at the neighbors you can just turn it off

data.name: Zombie Attack Bunny
data.description: You're nobody till somebunny bites you. Summon a zombie bunny by your side that will hop after and attack enemy that gets too close. He's loyal and will walk wherever you click nearby and attack anybody you wish!

data.name: Birthday Dance Party Potion
data.description: Quite possibly our most dancetastic dance potion yet!  Dance like nobody's watching!

data.name: Korblox: DeathSpeaker's Zombie Creator
data.description: This once powerful wizard dagger, tainted by the DeathSpeaker blood now serves the Korbloxians well! Said to be wielded only by the strongest DeathSpeakers of Korbloxia, the dagger creates a Zombie of its victims and helps its Master do his bidding.

data.name: Graffiti Skateboard
data.description: Keep it fresh with this skateboard.

data.name: Sword of the Seas
data.description: Click to slash at your foes and deal 15 damage.  When you are tired of this, unleash the wrath of the waves upon your foes with the special attack key 'Q'

data.name: Mechatronic Spider
data.description: All you makers out there will appreciate all the effort that went into making this robotic spider!  Send the spider (and his friends) to attack your foes.

data.name: Gearworks Sword
data.description: A swift sword that does 12 to 18 damage per hit. Watch out for the steam though!

data.name: Blimp Trophy
data.description: Jump higher with the Blimp Trophy as you complete the Nickelodeon Kids’ Choice Awards missions. Catch the show Saturday, March 24 at 8/7c

data.name: Zombie Friend Fred
data.description: Friends don't let friends eat brains...so maybe Fred isn't exactly your friend...

data.name: Black Panther - Claws
data.description: The power of the gauntlets will get you further, faster for the Innovation Event! Be sure to see Marvel Studio’s Black Panther in theaters February 16!

data.name: Misfortune Cookie
data.description: It's not going to bring you luck but it might be fun.

data.name: Light Face Melting Guitar
data.description: That heavenly sound that will bring the house (and people's faces) down.

data.name: Magnificent Lion
data.description: You've befriended the king of beasts, and now you two will ride together. Hop on and control using 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D' or the arrow keys. Hit space to jump. Shift to charge; ctrl to dismount.

data.name: Double Fire Laser Gun
data.description: Click to fire two laser pellets. If they hit an enemy, they deal 15 damage. The 'Q' and 'L' keys toggle a light, and the 'X', 'C' toggle crouching and crawling.

data.name: Banjo
data.description:
I want to be a rock star, and travel really far, and buy / me a big expensive car. /
And make lots of money and find me a honey. /
And live in nice big house where it's sunny. /
With a pool and I'll be cool. /
I'll always have a gig cause I'll be big. /
I'll have parties and friends and places to go, /
The only problem is I play the banjo. - Ryan Shupe

data.name: Spec Zeta Biograft Energy Sword
data.description: After the tremendous success of the Epsilon sword, only one person was left who understood how to make energy swords.  This is largely due to the scientists testing the swords on one another in an effort to create the best product possible (and to keep all the profit for themselves).  The last scientist left standing created only 200 of these before he was spawn killed by a noob holding his own sword.

data.name: Bloxster 2XZ
data.description: 25% faster than the Bloxster 2XH. You fancy!

data.name: Floating Thingumajig
data.description: A truly revolutionary device that follows you no matter where you or your imagination wanders.

data.description: Pop out at your enemies when they least expect it.  This magical elixir makes you completely invisible to other players for a limited amount of time.

data.name: Sabertooth Attack Friend

data.name: Snowball Gloves
data.description: Summon a snowball in your hands and throw it at friends! Click and you hold your arms out together and a create a snowball in thin air. Click again to throw it, like any other snowball!

data.name: Sir Scaresalot
data.description: A good knight always carries on until the job is done. Equip to spawn this loyal ghost knight by your side. He'll attack at your command.

data.name: Bloxdor's Ray Gun
data.description: Speak softly and carry a big ray gun. Fire neon red laser projectiles which instantly vaporize your enemies! Very powerful so it has a pretty long reload. Part of the Bloxdor Champion of the Stars package.

data.name: Carrot Slingshot
data.description: Sling deadly carrots at your enemies!! Click to release the string and launch a carrot in the direction of your cursor. Roughly 10 damage is dealt to any enemies hit.

data.name: Dread Dark Wizard Staff
data.description: Mighty is the hand that holds this dark power. Click to launch deadly reddish orbs at your enemies; dealing 20 damage each! You can fire up to 6 at a time before being hit with a short cooldown. Part of the Dread Dark Wizard package.

data.name: Eveningstar: Bringer of Dusk
data.description: Legend tells of a cursed mace appearing in conflicts from time immemorial. A terrible darkness radiates from it as whispers swarm your mind.

data.name: Big Bug Net
data.description: Is someone BUGGING you? Well tell them to buzz off! Swing the net at your enemies, either stunning them in their place temporarily, or literally- catch them inside the net! Enemies will literally shrink and appear in the net for a short while unable to do anything!

data.name: Deluxe Coil Gun
data.description: With lightning in your hand, the future is yours! Shoot electric blue beams of electricity at enemies. Deals 15 damage per hit and stuns enemies for a moment!

data.name: Emerald Claw: The Envious Club
data.description: Im not sure where he got this, I don't think I want to know either... Click to bash this upon your enemies heads! Dealing 20 to 30 damage! You will either whack your enemy or swing overhead. Double click to forcefully swing from above; dealing massive damage and temporarily stunning them!  Part of the Emerald Claw: The Envious package.
