data.description: Shoot yourself into space with this awesome pararocket.  Then glide back down with your own parachute!

data.name: Footbag
data.description: Have some colorful fun with this colorful footbag! Pull off some cool moves and show it off to your friends! Time to enjoy the summer!

data.name: Discus 2012
data.description: Throw this discus far enough and you'll get an explosive reward.

data.name: High Five
data.description: I've got a high five with your name on it! Only if your name is 5...

data.name: Ceramic Potion
data.description: Dust from Atlantis, ground unicorn horn, and cookie crumbs. This potion increases your max health, at a slight cost to speed.

data.name: Seashell Snare
data.description: She sells seashells by the seashore.   But she doesn't mess around.  This shell is a trap that will ensnare any enemies that get too close!

data.name: Club Boates Disco Ball
data.description: Summon your very own club and dance anywhere!

data.name: Super Strong Man
data.description: Eating these veggies will make you big and strong and ready to power slam anybody!

data.name: Deputy Bobby's Cowboy Boots
data.description: Sheriff Bobby runs faster and jumps higher than any cowboy in the west. That's why he always gets his man.

data.name: Sleepy Song Bird
data.description: What a sweet song.... zzzzz.  How can anyone stay awake when they hear this sweet music?  They can't!

data.name: ROBLOXIAN Damage Orb
data.description: Equip these and leave them by pressing 'Q' in your wake—they only do 20 hit points of damage to other players, but each time they hit an orb, you gain a 60% speed buff!

data.name: Snowplow
data.description: Click on a player to chase them with your snowplow and push them away from you.

data.name: Retro Candy
data.description: Put your enemies to sleep with six pieces of this delicious retro candy.

data.name: Deluxe Slime Ray
data.description: He slimed me! A rapid fire slime gun; can fire quickly with a short reload time. Shoot projectiles of slime at your opponents which do 8 damage upon striking them and obscure their screen in slime temporarily!

data.name: Crocopal
data.description: One click will have your foes running from this adorably vicious crocodile pal.

data.name: Attack Racket
data.description: They can't hit what they can't touch! Swing this tennis racket, firing flaming tennis balls at your opponent! If hit, the tennis balls deal 20 damage per hit.

data.name: Judge Underwood's Gavel
data.description: No you're out of order!  This whole trial's out of order!

data.name: Colonel's Cavalry Sabre
data.description: Yee Haw!

data.name: Golden Shuriken
data.description: As graceful as the falling leaves, as fast as the hunted gazelle.

data.name: Metal Cog Shuriken
data.description: Use your collection of cogs as dangerous shuriken! Each hit does 25 damage.

data.name: Polar Bear Attack Claws
data.description: Slash at your enemies with these polar bear claws to do 15 damage. Double click to grab a player and do 40 damage.

data.name: Sleep Wand
data.description: You're getting very sleepy!  Put your nearby foes to sleep for a short while.

data.name: Hedgehog Horde
data.description: Release the hedgehogs!  Click on enemies to get your hedgehogs to attack them!

data.name: Celtic Throwing Stars
data.description: Small enough to hide in a leprechaun's pocket, deadly enough to belong in an assassin's.

data.name: Watermelon Launcher
data.description: Click to launch ripe summer watermelons at your foes!  If hit, your target will take 15 damage and have a screen covered in Watermelon splatters!

data.name: Four-In-A-Row
data.description: Play a quick game of Four-In-A-Row with a nearby player! (Get close to another player and click on them to start a game - they need to accept your challenge for the game to start)

data.name: 8-Bit Crossbow
data.description: This 8-bit crossbow deals 20 damage upon impact on a player.

data.name: Festive Laser Blaster
data.description: Jingle bells, jingle bells, blast them all with lasers! Fire red and green projectiles that do five damage per hit.

data.name: Bruin Mount
data.description: Ride in bearly affordable style. This baby bear will take you anywhere you want to go.

data.name: Beef Wellington Launcher
data.description: Burgers are for the common folk, but beef wellington is next level delicious. In fact, they are so delicious that your foes will eat them until it's painful and does damage.

data.name: Staff of Double Disasters
data.description: Swing this mighty staff above your head to summon double disasters!  A tornado and tsunami will trouble your foes while you are safe.

data.name: The Sword of Shai
data.description: Your destiny awaits!  This sword has five different attacks, each does a varying amount of damage- anywhere from 6-12 points per hit.  One's fate is often not clear - so it's fitting that this sword of fate will will obscure the vision of your foes with a sand storm when they get within 20 studs of you.

data.name: Attack Snake Staff
data.description: Click to summon a bunch of snakes around you which slither toward whatever location you desire.

data.name: Skipper Seal
data.description: Your first mate has got your back.  Even when he's a seal.  Click on a foe to have skipper seal slap him silly.

data.name: Hot Chocolate Launcher
data.description: In the right hands, hot cocoa can be quite dangerous.  Shoot a stream of burning hot cocoa at your foes - if you hit them, they'll take 50 damage and their screen will be splattered with chocolatey goodness.

data.name: Bunny Ninja Master Sai
data.description: The great bunny ninja masters could slice very quickly, as well as hop great distances through the air. They could even channel powerful bunny bombs to fling their enemies far from them.

data.name: Battle Sleighs!
data.description: Just in time for winter - battle sleighs are here! Let the sleighing begin!

data.name: Penguin Shooter
data.description: Left click to fire a baby penguin from the launcher. The baby penguin will jump around, dealing up to 10 damage each second for 10 seconds. You can have 15 baby penguins running around at a time for a full on penguin swarm!

data.name: Pirate Lieutenant's Cutlass
data.description: A mighty sword she be.  Only the mightiest of men might hope to wield her gracefully.

data.name: Battle Wagons!
data.description: You're a pioneer, fighting for land and survival.  You've got one problem - other wagons stealing your resources! How do you solve it? Battle Wagons! Battle wagons is played with two Robloxians.  Each places his wagons on a grid that the other player can't see.  Then you guess where the other player's wagons are and fire away.  You sunk my battle wagon!

data.name: Bombo's Survival Raig Table
data.description: When Bombo gets mad, he gets really mad, explosively mad!

data.name: Angry Attack Squirrel
data.description: This fuzzy little guy attacks at your command!  He'll follow you around and attack anyone you click, doing ten damage per second.

data.name: Starfish Shooter
data.description: Launches a starfish, and it will stick to your target.  Shoot too many starfish and it might obscure your opponent's vision!

data.name: Big Apple Launcher
data.description: Launch explosive apples at your foes.  In the city, you must fight to survive!

data.name: Magic Carrot
data.description: This carrot packs a major rabbit punch!

data.name: Turkey Cannon
data.description: Shoots live turkeys!  Now if only we had a water gun that shot cranberry sauce...and ovens?

data.name: Beach Battle Sword
data.description: The battle for beach supremacy is on!  Send walls of water crashing on your enemies.

data.name: Hypnocannon
data.description: You're getting very sleepy!  And slow!  You're in control with the hypnocannon!

data.name: Saw Sword
data.description: Those trees had it coming!

data.name: Laser-saw
data.description: Chain saws are so yesterday on Earth.  The future is now with this laser saw.  Tired of just sawing through your enemies with lasers? Double click to activate the special laser shooting attack.

data.name: Boss Bunny Bow and Arrow
data.description: The boss bunny is the boss for a reason.  Boss bunny never misses a shot. Use his bow and arrow to fire arrows that do 35 damage per hit.

data.name: Music Blaster
data.description: Music is destroy this generation!  Literally!  This awesome gun shoots your foes to do 10 points of damage - it's music to your ears!  Don't forget to try out this item's special by hitting the 'Q' key.

data.name: Earth's Might Staff
data.description: Summon a heavy boulder to drop on your enemies.  If you click and hold, the boulder will gain more force!

data.name: Steamgun
data.description: This powerful steamgun emits... you guessed it... steam!  Shoot a stream of steam at your foes to do damage.

data.name: Crate of Snakes
data.description: Snakes.  Why'd it have to be snakes?

data.name: Bejeweled Sword of Great Fury
data.description: Do you see red or blue?  This fierce sword lets you switch between Ruby and Sapphire attacks.  In Ruby mode you deal 40 damage per hit, but take 15 damage yourself. In Sapphire mode you do 15 damage per hit, but can strike at a great speed, and heal yourself with each hit you land.

data.name: Helper Cannon
data.description: Even in his demise, still helpful.

data.name: Axe of Blinding Justice
data.description: Chop through your foes, doing 20 damage with each swing of this mighty blade. As you wound your enemies you gain light which you can use to set off a solar energy explosion- doing 45 damage per hit.

data.name: Dynamically Lit Bow and Arrow
data.description: Light up the night with this dynamic bow and arrow set.  One hit does 22 damage, but charge the bow and you'll quadruple the damage.

data.name: Stinky Underwear Launcher
data.description: Avoid the stinky underwear at all costs!

data.name: The Break Up
data.description: It's called the break up because it breaks things.

data.name: EMP Shockmine
data.description: Shock the gear out of your opponents hands.

data.name: EKoSS Bow and Arrow
data.description: The Emerald Knights are known for their legendary prowess with a bow. This bow and arrow do between 15 to 55 damage, depending on how long it has been charged.

data.name: Zombie Axe
data.description: Does 15 damage per swipe and summons some Zombies to eat your enemies brains.

data.name: jmargh's Arm Cannon
data.description: Thar be danger ahead!  Shoot cannonballs at your foes. Hold down the mouse to charge the cannon to do maximum damage!

data.name: Garbage Can Shield and Wooden Sword Set
data.description: Sometimes you have to improvise....

data.name: The Sea's Revenge
data.description: These are the tears that launched a thousand ships.  Ghost ships.  Into your enemies.

data.name: Primeval Crossbow
data.description: This item gets better with more use!  Shoot arrows at your foes, and the more you use it the faster you are able to reload it! Eventually you'll be firing so quickly that you'll unleash the bow's primeval rage!  You'll hear the mighty dinosaur roar and the arrows will flame as you unleash tons of arrows at once.

data.name: Inglaciator -6000
data.description: Why -6000?  Because it launches an icy sphere of doom that is -6000 degrees.  Click and hold to charge up your icy projectile and release to launch it. When your ice hits - it will create an icy ball that grows over time. Anyone hit by the ice will take 30 damage.  Your foes' chances of survival? Absolute zero.

data.name: Egg Fuse Bomb
data.description: Get ready for a serious eggsplosion!

data.name: Ninja Darts
data.description: Unleash the fury of a million darts on your opponents.  Okay - so you'd have to throw it a few times to launch a million.  But the fury is real?  Yeah...what he said.

data.name: Illuminating Spear of Revengeance
data.description: There are people who will tell you that revengeance is not a thing, but those are people have never felt the way you do.... or they own dictionaries. Revengeance is yours with this spear that both stabs and charges up for a super powerful attack.

data.name: Laserface
data.description: Rapid fire laser beams directly from your face to your foes.  Each hit does 5 damage, which adds up quickly as you rapidly fire a weapon from your face!

data.name: Steampunk Jetpack
data.description: Steam is the power of the future! Use this steampunk jetpack to glide around ROBLOX with ease.

data.name: Korblox Evil Eye
data.description: The Korblox place their evil eye on walls or even directly on enemies to spy on them at every turn. Then when the moment is right....kaboom!

data.name: Implosion Bomb
data.description: Click once and then toss the bomb onto the ground- away from yourself of course! The implosion bomb will beep for five seconds and then implode. Everything flies inward and anyone hit will take 100 damage points!

data.name: The Drop
data.description: It's time to drop the bass... on your foes... Drop this awesome bass on your friends or foes when it gets too heavy.

data.name: Wasp Wings
data.description: Equip this item and get wasp wings that give you speed, and more importantly the ability to charge your enemies with a deadly wasp dash.  Any hit while in wasp dash mode does 80 damage on impact!

data.name: Homemade Jet pack
data.description: Harness the power of steam to send you soaring through the skies of ROBLOX.

data.name: Knights of RedCliff: Battle Horn
data.description: Blow thy horn and blast thy foes as the noble RedCliff Eagles swarm unto the battlefield doing justice to thy goals.

data.name: Bamboo Dart Blowgun
data.description: From the infamous Shadow Ninjas of Robloxia comes this blowgun capable of firing 3 deadly darts at insane speeds.

data.name: DarkAge Ninjas: Combat Potion
data.description:
The DarkAge Ninjas are masters of hand to hand combat that none but the fiercest of warriors can handle. 

Drink this potion to increase your vitality to two fold, and to learn to spin kick, flash kick and charge kick in the face, decimating anyone who tries to fight you.

data.name: Spikesplosion
data.description: If you're not shooting off spikes, what are you doing?

data.name: Pigs Boson Collider
data.description: Utilizing the Large Hilarity Collider, researchers created the conditions immediately after the Big Chuckle and discovered the emergence of the Pigs Boson, the fundamental particle of funny that will destroy your target for hilarity.

data.name: Magmarealm Crossbow
data.description: This ain't your granny's crossbow.

data.name: Cursed Fire Flame Thrower
data.description: "We didn't start the fire..."  Oh wait...yes you did. And it's not just regular fire - this fire is cursed

data.name: Snow and Arrow
data.description: Click and hold to pull the arrow back further, charging it and increasing its damage. Minimum damage is 5, and maximum is 66.

data.name: Razor Sharp Looks
data.description: If looking good was a crime, you'd be deadly. Also the blades help.  Click to throw in the direction of your cursor. Blades will pop out of the sides of the fedora and spin toward its target.

data.name: Exploding Arrow Crimson Crossbow
data.description: This crimson crossbow fires an arrow that sticks to the first thing it hits and explodes after about 2 seconds. The explosion deals between 10 and 110 damage based on how long the arrow was flying through the air.

data.name: Redcliff Battleaxe
data.description: When evil looms, Redcliff Knights answer the call, with this might axe! Click to slash enemies, unleash a mighty lunge attack to do more damage.

data.name: Star Hammer
data.description: Great men don't watch the stars, great men forge the stars.

data.name: Deluxe Snowball Cannon 3000
data.description: Faster than every other snowball cannon on the market, the Deluxe Snowball Cannon 3000 can fire multiple shots in quick succession.

data.name: Knights of Redcliff: Deluxe Sword and Shield Set
data.description: Don't let this simple, elegant blade fool you.  This is the most deadly Redcliff sword yet!

data.name: Bluesea Soarer
data.description: This powerful blue dragon will follow you around and shoot fiery death balls at your enemies.

data.name: Korblox Flying Oblivion Horn
data.description: Korbloxians use this trumpet to summon death from above.  Once the trumpet sounds, Skeletal birds swoop in to destroy the Korblox's foes.

data.name: billylones' ROBLOX Tablet
data.description: Winner: billylones. ROBLOX will be in touch to redeem this prize. Void if sold, traded, or deleted.

data.name: The Tormentor's Axe
data.description: Only the very best escape the hot steel of the Tormentor's Axe!

data.name: Emerald Scatterblaster 2000
data.description: To make ammo for the Emerald Scatterblaster you heat emeralds until they're vapor.  Load the emerald vapor into the scatterblaster and you're good to go!

data.name: Wraith's Screech Potion
data.description: His scream pierces all that come near him.

data.name: Crimson Double Threat
data.description: Double your threat, double your fun!

data.name: Scythe of Singularity
data.description: This mighty weapon will leave you spinning.  Literally.

data.name: Zeus's Lightning Bolt Staff
data.description: Hurl lightning at your enemies.  Because they probably deserve it.

data.name: Otterhead Longsword
data.description: And you thought the Otterhead Shortsword was cool!  Hit 'Q' to get the sword to spin in a circle and do 20 damage per hit. Otherwise, click to attack and do 10-15 damage per hit!

data.name: Mardi Gras Sword
data.description: Laissez les bons temps rouler!  Your enemies don't stand a chance against this festive sword. Celebrate your victory over your enemies with a little confetti party.

data.name: Enchanted Bat Flying Potion
data.description: Soar above your opponents with this epic bat potion.

data.name: Sword of the Autumnal Winds
data.description: Leafing your enemies in your dust....

data.name: Festive Artemis Bow
data.description: Because- why not? When fired, arrows leave a candy cane beam trailing behind. Randomly colored ornaments spawn around where the arrow hit. This is one festive range attacked!

data.name: Sword of the Summer Sun
data.description: The pain of a million sunburns...

data.name: Dark Alien Hatchling
data.description: When you see this egg - you better run!  As soon as the alien hatches, it's too late!

data.name: Zombification Injection
data.description: Steal other people's life force to transform yourself into a powerful and angry zombie.  As a zombie, use your powerful hammer to do 40 damage per hit to other players.

data.name: Retribution Ray
data.description: The forces of retribution are always listening. They never sleep.

data.name: Glory Launcher 2012
data.description: With this heat seeking missile launcher, your foes don't stand a chance.

data.name: Sharp Shark Sword
data.description: Do 15 to 35 damage per swing with this amazing Sharp Shark Sword (say that 10 times fast!)  Click and hold to do the special attack, which will unleash a tsunami, complete with hungry ,that you will ride for several seconds.  Anyone hit by the wave or sharks will take massive damage!

data.name: Superhero Potion
data.description: It's a bird, it's a plane, it's a flying Robloxian shooting fireballs?

data.name: Catapult
data.description: Launching projectiles the old fashion way.
